task.summary: Default task
Created base of the app
Created button that adds option fields to the poll creator
Save poll button now creates an Array of strings containing text from the edit fields - Created PollBuilder class
Added finish method to EditorActivity
Created pollView row layout for Manager activity - Added a functionless adapter to pollList array in Manager
Added ViewHolder inner class to ManagerActvitiy
Created custom adapter to dynamically show list of current polls
Added working delete button to the manager activity
Generated links to the other activities from each row - Can pass polls through links - Created HashMapAdapter class
Implemented ViewHolder in PollListAdapter
Finished PollAdapter - ResultsActivity now displays poll stats
Fixed formatting on Manager pollList
Added PollQuestion field to Poll class and implemented it throughout app
Added PollVoteAdapter Class - Reformated VoteActivity and Vote Screen layout
MVP hit - Votes counts now show on result screen
Refactored all of the Java portion of the project
Removed an unused variable and whitespace
PollBuilder now drops identical choices and Editor displays a toast when the user creates an empty option
Returned returnToMainFunction within VoteActivity
Added .gitignore file
Changed them to HoloDark and added Menu bar icons
Back button no longer crashes on vote and edit activity
Poll List now populates from the top of screen
Added Parse to application - created custom Application class
Menu bar now links to About and Help pages
Added content to Help and About pages
Moved the new poll button to the action bar
Migrated to Material theme from Holo - Backwards compatible
